snippet.title: Best VGM 1740 - Blaster Master - Fortress (Stage 3)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 228 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PKno6qPQEJg

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Blaster Master (1988)
Fortress (Stage 3)
Naoki Kodaka
